sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Pytest as Pytest runner
    participant MySQLProc as mysql_proc fixture (session scope)
    participant MySQL as mysql fixture (function scope)
    participant MySQLServer as MySQL server
    participant TestDB as Per-test DB (created by mysql fixture)

    Pytest->>MySQLProc: first test requests mysql fixture dependency
    MySQLProc->>MySQLServer: initialize datadir and start server
    Note right of MySQLProc: Server starts once per test session
    loop per test
        Pytest->>MySQL: request mysql fixture
        MySQL->>MySQLServer: CREATE DATABASE {TEST_DB_NAME}
        MySQL->>MySQLServer: USE {TEST_DB_NAME}
        Pytest->>TestDB: run test against selected DB
        MySQL->>MySQLServer: teardown: DROP DATABASE IF EXISTS {TEST_DB_NAME}
    end
    MySQLProc->>MySQLServer: shutdown server at session end
